9. Running the Project
Open two terminals.
Terminal 1 – Backend
cd backend
source venv/bin/activate
python main.py
Backend will start at: http://localhost:8000
Terminal 2 – Frontend
cd frontend
npm run dev
Frontend will start at: http://localhost:3000

